00062 void FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionDataTest::testRead()
00063 {
00064         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::Read("../../parsers/data/CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00065         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chp != NULL);
00066         FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionData *sigChp = FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionData::FromBase(chp); 
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp != NULL);
00068 
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp->GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp->GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00071         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp->GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00072         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp->GetEntryCount() == 2);
00073         
00074         ParameterNameValueTypeList params = sigChp->GetAlgParams();
00075         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00076         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it=params.begin();
00077         ParameterNameValueType &param = *it;
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00079         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00080 
00081         params = sigChp->GetSummaryParams();
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00083         it=params.begin();
00084         param = *it;
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00087 
00088         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationDetectionData e;
00089         sigChp->GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(0, e);
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00091     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.quantification == 10.0f);
00092     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.pvalue == 0.10f);
00093         sigChp->GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(1, e);
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.quantification == 20.0f);
00096     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.pvalue == 0.20f);
00097 
00098         
00099         delete sigChp;
00100 }
